# ChapterDock 📚

ChapterDock is a full-stack book review platform that allows users to create accounts, log in securely, and share reviews about books they have read.

## Features

- User authentication (Signup/Login)
- Secure session management
- Add and manage books
- Rate books
- Write and publish reviews
- Responsive user interface
- PostgreSQL database integration
- Supabase-powered backend services

## Tech Stack

- Node.js
- Express.js
- PostgreSQL
- Supabase
- EJS
- CSS

## Future Improvements

- Book cover uploads
- Search and filtering
- User profiles
- Like and comment system
- Bookmark/Favorites feature
- Pagination
- Recommendation engine
